name: Her Arch Makes Heaven:Twenty Two
description:
Egyptian religion is unique in the genders of its deities of earth and sky. As the goddess of the sky, Nut swallowed the sun in the evening and gave birth to it again in the morning. 
she generally takes the form of a naked woman covered with stars, holding her body up in an arch, facing downwards. Her arms and legs were the pillars of the sky, and her hands and feet were thought to touch the ground at the four cardinal points on the horizon.
